title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 325-6.14 - Dispute forum rules
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 325-6.14 - Dispute forum rules

State Regulations

All parties subject to the provisions of this Subpart
shall be subject to any rules promulgated by the dispute forum with respect to
its own internal procedures regarding the administration of disputed requests
for reimbursement, to the extent that such rules are not inconsistent with this

Subpart. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12
